        <div id="successPhase" class="hidden">
            <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExOHp1eXFmZzRreXJ4ZzRreXJ4ZzRreXJ4ZzRreXJ4ZzRreXJ4ZyZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/l41lI4bYy3ZInA6Yw/giphy.gif" alt="Celebration">
            <h1>Yay! I knew you'd say yes! ‚ù§Ô∏è</h1>
